# Semgrep exclusions for Nakama Protocol.
# Implements .claude/rules/ci-gates.md "T2-2 design constraint".
#
# Project mixes Russian prose (docs / comments / commit messages) with
# English code per CLAUDE.md "Output conventions". Semgrep's homoglyph
# rule (Cyrillic + Latin) fires on every Cyrillic character — this is
# intentional, not an attack vector. We scan code, not prose.

# Markdown / documentation
*.md
docs/
.claude/

# Build artifacts (target dirs already in .gitignore but defensive)
target/
nakama/target/
node_modules/
clients/ts/dist/

# Lockfiles (not code)
Cargo.lock
clients/ts/package-lock.json
clients/ts/yarn.lock

# Test fixtures
**/test-ledger/
**/*.json.bak

# IDE / OS
.idea/
.DS_Store
